                <h1>Unveiling Home Depot’s Founders: The Story Behind the Brand</h1>
                <p>Home Depot founder Bernie Marcus, alongside Arthur Blank, established the home improvement giant in 1978. Their vision was to create a one-stop shop for DIY enthusiasts and professionals alike. Marcus believed in empowering customers with knowledge and resources, which became a hallmark of the Home Depot experience. Today, it stands as a front-runner in the retail market.</p>
